        <p class="text-[15px] text-heading font-medium leading-relaxed m-0"><strong>Key insight:</strong> No single tool tracks all AI platforms comprehensively. The best approach for most businesses is to start with manual testing, use Google Search Console for AI Overview data, and add a specialist tool like AwarenessAI or Otterly when you are ready to invest in ongoing monitoring.</p>
